'''斯坦'''（'''sthène'''、'''sthéne'''<ref name="Fenna p.281">{{cite book|last=Fenna|first=Donald|title=A Dictionary Of Weights, Measures, and Units|url=https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofweig0000fenn|year=2002|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford, England|isbn=019-860522-6|page=[https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofweig0000fenn/page/281 281]|chapter=m. t. s. system|quote='''sthéne''' ''force''. Symbol sn. ''Metric-m.t.s''. That which produces an acceleration of 1 m·s<sup>−2</sup> when applied to a mass of 1 t[onne] = 1 kN. Originally called the '''funal''' when proposed by the British Association in 1876, it was renamed by 1914. It was authorized in France by statute of 1919 as part of the m–t–s system. }}</ref>或'''sthene'''<ref name="Fenna p.109">{{cite book|last=Fenna|first=Donald|title=A Dictionary Of Weights, Measures, and Units|url=https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofweig0000fenn|year=2002|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford, England|isbn=019-860522-6|page=[https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofweig0000fenn/page/190 190]|chapter=m. t. s. system|quote='''m.t.s system ''' ('''Metric-m.t.s.,''' also '''MTS system''')…In the m.t.s. system the unit of force, for example, is the sthene, which gives an acceleration of 1 m·s<sup>−2</sup> to a body of 1 t[onne]…}}</ref>）縮寫為'''sn'''，是[[米-公噸-秒制|米-公噸-秒制]]中[[力|力]]的單位，是在1919年引入法國的<ref>{{cite book|title=Scientific American Monthly|url=https://archive.org/details/scientificameric41419newy|year=1920|publisher=[[Scientific_American|Scientific American]]|location=New York|page=[https://archive.org/details/scientificameric41419newy/page/152 152]|chapter=New units in the metric system—legally adopted in France|issn=0740-6495|oclc=1765222}}</ref>。此單位在1876年由{{le|英国学术协会|British Association}}提出時，其名稱為funal，在1914年改為目前的名稱<ref name="Fenna p.281"/>。[[米-公噸-秒制|米-公噸-秒制]]被後來的[[米-公斤-秒制|米-公斤-秒制]]及[[國際單位制|國際單位制]]所取代，此單位也很少被使用<ref name="Fenna p.109"/>。

